context:
KR:
&lt;어떻게 된 거야? 날 대신해서 싸워준다고 했잖아!&gt;
EN:
&lt;What the hell is going on? You said you’ll fight in my stead!&gt;

KR:
&lt;그, 그래. 이렇게 되기를 기다리고 있었던 건가?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Oookay. So you were waiting for this?&gt;

KR:
&lt;비장의 수가 있는 거지?&gt;
EN:
&lt;You have some hidden card up your sleeve, right?&gt;

KR:
&lt;대체… 뭘 어쩌라는 거야?&gt;
EN:
&lt;What… what am I supposed to do?&gt;

KR:
&lt;의기양양하게 등장해서 죽어나가는 꼴이라니…&gt;
EN:
&lt;They jumped in triumphantly only to die like flies…&gt;

KR:
&lt;으… 아까 저자의 말을 따라 한 다음부터 옛 기억이 전혀 나질 않아.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Gah… I can’t remember a thing about the past since I repeated what she said.&gt;

KR:
&lt;나는… 이렇게 죽는 건가?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Is this… how I die?&gt;

KR:
&lt;뭐야… 너도 저놈들이랑 한패야?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Who are… Are you one of them?&gt;

KR:
&lt;하지만 다들 이미…&gt;
EN:
&lt;You’re too late, they’re already…&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#b01c37&gt;심장이 여러 갈래로 쪼개지는 듯한 고통이 불현듯 엄습한다.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#b01c37&gt;I’m suddenly overwhelmed by a sharp pain in my chest, as though my heart were being torn asunder.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#b01c37&gt;그 뒤를 이어 늑골이, 대장이, 위와 폐가.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#b01c37&gt;Followed by flashes in the ribs, intestines, stomach, and lungs.&lt;/color&gt;
